# Buildroot hash file for the ados-agent-lite release tarball.
#
# Buildroot rebuilds the package on every release-tarball SHA bump, and the
# .hash file pins the exact bytes we expect from GitHub Releases. Override
# ADOS_AGENT_LITE_VERSION in the defconfig to pin a stable release; bump
# both the sha256 line and the LICENSE line below when you do.
#
# Generate locally:
#   curl -L <release-url>/ados-agent-lite-lite-agent-main-armv7-unknown-linux-musleabihf.tar.gz \
#     | sha256sum
#   sha256sum LICENSE
#
# Format: <algo>  <hex>  <filename>
#
# Until the lite-image-v* tag pipeline cuts its first stable release, this file
# carries placeholders. The CI workflow at .github/workflows/luckfox-image-build.yml
# substitutes real digests on tag.

# sha256  PLACEHOLDER  ados-agent-lite-lite-agent-main-armv7-unknown-linux-musleabihf.tar.gz
# sha256  PLACEHOLDER  LICENSE
